   README 
   ======

This is custom grant type to retrieve access token by providing a cookie which is returned from forgerock OpenAM.

This has been tested in WSO2IS 5.3.0 & APIM 2.1.0 with the cookies provided by OpenAM 13.5.0
   
1. Implementation details is in here [1]

2. Use maven 3 to build the project.

3. Configuration details also can find from there [1]


[1]

<SupportedGrantType>
<GrantTypeName>openam_cookie</GrantTypeName>
<GrantTypeHandlerImplClass>org.soasecurity.wso2.oauth2.openam.cookie.grant.OpenAMCookieGrantHandler</GrantTypeHandlerImplClass>
<GrantTypeValidatorImplClass>org.soasecurity.wso2.oauth2.openam.cookie.grant.OpenAMCookieGrantValidator</GrantTypeValidatorImplClass>
</SupportedGrantType>
